    "label": "Projected end-of-week cash",
    "number": 65714.0,
    "paragraph": "We close this week at roughly $65,714 available across all accounts after $37K in external payments and $33K in internal management fee and insurance transfers. GRP projects to $-3,654 after receiving June management fees from all properties \u2014 still negative due to pending transactions already in the bank that precede this week. Winterwood and Country Aire are also thin after their open lot insurance shares and need intercompany support from Decade Acres or Four Seasons. The WW home closings remain the most important near-term cash event for rebuilding GRP."
  },
